    But you can have anything
    from here to there.

00:29.964 --> 00:32.398
               Come on,
               don't be a dick.

00:33.466 --> 00:36.135
    Look, I'm sorry,
    but I have to go

00:36.137 --> 00:38.737
  with what's on the receipt.
  Rules are rules.

00:38.739 --> 00:42.641
              Just... forget it.

00:42.643 --> 00:44.943
        We'll just get some of
        those plastic handcuffs.

00:46.379 --> 00:47.913
Oh, there you go.

00:47.915 --> 00:52.084
You can play by the rules
and still have fun.

00:52.086 --> 00:53.519
          Here.

00:53.521 --> 00:56.155
    Here's a few tokens
    on the house.

00:57.323 --> 00:58.891
                       Let's go!

